superharness (0.2.0-1) noble; urgency=low

  * Initial release.
  * Autonomous multi-agent orchestrator for AI coding agents via tmux.
  * Features: spawn/read/send worker panes, git worktree isolation,
    task dependencies, loop detection, health monitoring, away mode,
    checkpoint/resume, and Homebrew/AUR/PPA publishing infrastructure.

